README
This bot is used to log messages in irc chats, sending these logs to email addresses and checking the last encounter with user.

usage: bot.py [-h] [-s SERVER] [-p PORT] [-n NICK] [-i IDENT] [-r REAL]
                [-c CHANNEL] [-D] [-address M_ADDRESS] [-server M_SERVER]
                [-username M_USERNAME] [-password M_PASSWORD] [-plugin PLUGIN]

optional arguments:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  -s SERVER             Set IRC server
  -p PORT               Set IRC port
  -n NICK               Set IRC nick
  -i IDENT              Set IRC ident
  -r REAL               Set IRC real name
  -c CHANNEL            Set IRC channel
  -D                    Deactivate deamon
  -address M_ADDRESS    Mail address
  -server M_SERVER      Mail server
  -username M_USERNAME  Mail username
  -password M_PASSWORD  Mail password
  -plugin PLUGIN        used logging plugin
